&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Own connector coverage end-to-end: problem discovery through shipping, measuring, and iterating, framing problems as testable hypotheses and running efficient, fast experiments before committing engineering effort.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Sequence the roadmap to balance short-term commercial impact (revenue, retention, churn) with long-term product vision.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Shape the analysis rather than consume it: define the metrics and thresholds that drive decisions, not justify ones already made.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Work cross-functionally with Data Science, Engineering, Design, and Commercial, and build direct technical relationships with principal platform partners so that API changes, launches, and deprecations are anticipated before they hit customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Use AI tools daily (drafting, prototyping, analysis) and push the team to find new ways of working with them.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
